support email: lessontrackerforios@gmail.com

1. The landing page has a summary where you can track when your tests are and also see a report on your progress completion

2. the Lessons page allows you to add lessons with the pencil button in the navigation bar. once a lesson is selected a page will show which allows you to track each lessons in a detailed log

3. the ratings page allows you to track your skill level in a easy and simple way. Press your own rating for each topic and track how your feeling from lesson to lesson.
